        <item>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Physical Therapist Workforce and Patient Access Act of 2017</b></p> <p>This bill amends the Public Health Service Act to include physical therapy within the definition of &quot;primary health services&quot; for purposes of the National Health Service Corps. The bill makes physical therapists eligible for repayment of their educational loans in order to ensure an adequate supply of physical therapists.</p>]]></text>
